=========================================
django-fabdeploy-extensions
=========================================

This package extends functionality of django-fab-deploy
https://bitbucket.org/kmike/django-fab-deploy/overview

CAUTION: This package is not intended to be universal tool and might not suit your needs as a whole.
But you may find some of it's features useful and use them separately.

Features:

* UWSGI instead of Apache webserver
* Testing sources from mirror.yandex.ru
* Redis as cache backend by default
* Alternative approach for handling settings (split for evnironments, developers and applications)
* Sphinx fabric scripts
* multiple small improvements